{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/GeorgiGlashow/Basic.html#GeorgiGlashow.embedSMℤ₆\"><span class=\"name\">GeorgiGlashow</span>.<span class=\"name\">embedSMℤ₆</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The group embedding from `StandardModel.GaugeGroupℤ₆` to `GaugeGroupI` induced by `inclSM` by\nquotienting by the kernel `inclSM_ker`.\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/GeorgiGlashow/Basic.html#GeorgiGlashow.embedSMℤ₆","kind":"def","line":43,"name":"GeorgiGlashow.embedSMℤ₆","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L43-L48"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/GeorgiGlashow/Basic.html#GeorgiGlashow.inclSM_ker\"><span class=\"name\">GeorgiGlashow</span>.<span class=\"name\">inclSM_ker</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalLemma\">InformalLemma</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The kernel of the map `inclSM` is equal to the subgroup `StandardModel.gaugeGroupℤ₆SubGroup`.\n\nSee page 34 of https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/GeorgiGlashow/Basic.html#GeorgiGlashow.inclSM_ker","kind":"def","line":35,"name":"GeorgiGlashow.inclSM_ker","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L35-L41"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/GeorgiGlashow/Basic.html#GeorgiGlashow.inclSM\"><span class=\"name\">GeorgiGlashow</span>.<span class=\"name\">inclSM</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The homomorphism of the Standard Model gauge group into the Georgi-Glashow gauge group, i.e.,\nthe group homomorphism `SU(3) × SU(2) × U(1) → SU(5)` taking `(h, g, α)` to\n`blockdiag (α ^ 3 g, α ^ (-2) h)`.\n\nSee page 34 of https://math.ucr.edu/home/baez/guts.pdf\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/GeorgiGlashow/Basic.html#GeorgiGlashow.inclSM","kind":"def","line":25,"name":"GeorgiGlashow.inclSM","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L25-L33"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/GeorgiGlashow/Basic.html#GeorgiGlashow.GaugeGroupI\"><span class=\"name\">GeorgiGlashow</span>.<span class=\"name\">GaugeGroupI</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Meta/Informal/Basic.html#InformalDefinition\">InformalDefinition</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The gauge group of the Georgi-Glashow model, i.e., `SU(5)`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/BeyondTheStandardModel/GeorgiGlashow/Basic.html#GeorgiGlashow.GaugeGroupI","kind":"def","line":20,"name":"GeorgiGlashow.GaugeGroupI","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L20-L23"}}],"imports":["Init","PhysLean.Particles.StandardModel.Basic"],"instances":[],"name":"PhysLean.Particles.BeyondTheStandardModel.GeorgiGlashow.Basic"}